  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to compare the short-term (8 week) mean 24-hour intraocular
      pressure control and safety of TravTim fixed combination given once in the evening with
      placebo once in the morning versus TravTim given once in the morning with placebo once in the
      evening in patients with open-angle glaucoma.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
